data.description: Step into sophistication with this meticulously designed 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven boasting 2662 square feet of pure luxury. The heart of this home is its modern, upgraded kitchen. Immerse yourself in culinary delights with sleek stainless steel appliances, a design-forward aesthetic, and ample space for both cooking and entertaining. Whether you are a culinary enthusiast or a casual chef, this kitchen will inspire you. Two spacious family rooms offer endless possibilities for relaxation and entertainment. Embrace cozy family nights or host gatherings in these inviting spaces.   Additionally, a dedicated game room provides the perfect setting for leisure and play, creating a home that adapts to your lifestyle. Detail is overlooked, with blinds adorning every window, ensuring privacy and style. The 3-car garage provides secure parking and additional storage. Finally, a whole house filtration system by Elite Water Systems. GE 200 Series.
